  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "Because hardhat `tsconfig.json` files extend a base config that is outside the package, they cause TS language servers (e.g. in VSCode) to error, as the base config they extend is unavailable\r\n\r\nexample file:\r\nhttps://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/blob/48df7d37cccc8ce72233d73f2866c159c4212b74/packages/hardhat-core/src/tsconfig.json\r\n\r\nTo solve this, introduce a `.npmignore` file that excludes the tsconfig.json\r\n\r\n",
